Generate samples community-wide

Source: R/simulate_community.R
community_generate.Rd

Generate samples community-wide

community_generate(
  community_data_table,
  abundance_column_name = "speciestotal"
)

Arguments

community_data_table

dataframe containing at least one of aou, genus and species, or mean_size and a column for species abundances

abundance_column_name

character, the name of the column with species abundances. Defaults to "speciestotal"

Value

dataframe

Examples


demo_route_clean <- filter_bbs_survey(demo_route_raw)
community_generate(demo_route_clean)
